---
title: Chicken Marbella Includes recyclable aluminum tray
description: We made a classic "fancy" chicken dish weeknight-ready! Simply combine oregano-seasoned chicken, green olives, lemon, raisins, and vinegar in our convenient recyclable oven tray, and bake. Serve this sweet, tangy, briny, garlicky goodness over a hearty, lemony grain blend with a sprinkle of herbaceous parsley, and it's party time!
